<ul>

  <li>You give us relevant information to look for your bike, such as
  model, color, brand, and possibly a picture.</li>

  <li>WheresMoBike compares your description against bike
  advertisements online, selecting those that match the best. If some
  advertisement looks suspicious to you, you can contact the seller
  for further investigation.</li>

  <li> If your guess is proven correct, you can then point it out to
  the competent authorities so that legal measures can be taken.</li>

</ul>
